 <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="P:\Handbuch\corpus_satzuebersetzung.dita" xtrc="title:1;4:9">Translation</title>
 <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrf="P:\Handbuch\corpus_satzuebersetzung.dita" xtrc="shortdesc:1;5:13">How to insert translation for sentences</shortdesc>
 <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody " xtrf="P:\Handbuch\corpus_satzuebersetzung.dita" xtrc="conbody:1;6:11">
  <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="P:\Handbuch\corpus_satzuebersetzung.dita" xtrc="p:1;7:6">You can insert the translations for a single sentence in the bar below the Text Editor</p>
  <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,198,140"?>
  <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="P:\Handbuch\corpus_satzuebersetzung.dita" xtrc="p:2;9:6">Images/satz%C3%BCbersetzung.png<?oxy_custom_end?></p>
  <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="P:\Handbuch\corpus_satzuebersetzung.dita" xtrc="p:3;10:6">In a new text this bar is empty. Click the sentence you would like to translate and click the
   white bar to write your translation in it. Be sure to have selected the right language in the
   dropdown menu on the right. (<image href="Images/icons/full/icon16/locale.png" id="image_krw_wmv_nr" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " xtrf="P:\Handbuch\corpus_satzuebersetzung.dita" xtrc="image:1;13:28"/> : de, en, fr, es, ru). Then just type your translation for this
   sentence. In the standard view only one line wil be visible. Scroll up and down with the black
   triangles (on the right of the bar) if you need to see more. The complete translation of the text
   (as far as it is entered) will appear on the right of your BTS screen in the header <image href="Images/icons/full/icon16/locale.png" id="image_ozc_vnv_nr" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " xtrf="P:\Handbuch\corpus_satzuebersetzung.dita" xtrc="image:2;17:71"/> of the <xref href="oberflaeche_annotationsfenster.dita" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="P:\Handbuch\corpus_satzuebersetzung.dita" xtrc="xref:1;18:48">Annotation window</xref>
   (<?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>BUG: currently you have to
   refresh the view of your text to see the complete translation)<?oxy_custom_end?>.</p>
 </conbody>
